<p><strong>October Sprint #2</strong></p>
<p><strong></strong>The current sprint began <strong>Saturday, October 16</strong> and concludes <strong>Sunday, October 31</strong>. The <strong>Post Pandemic Challenge</strong> will end on December 31, 2021. After that date, Microsoft will charge you $30 to access its LinkedIn Learning library.</p>
<p>If you are ready to make a commitment to begin this free learning opportunity, simply review <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53267065">Post Pandemic Challenge &gt; Getting Started</a>.</strong> Then, post an Introduction stating what you will commit to work on during this two-week sprint. You can also post any barriers you might be encountering in shifting into post pandemic gear in the comments under <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53267065">Post Pandemic Challenge &gt; Getting Started</a></strong>.</p>
<p>What will you learn today?</p>
